  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Valet Simulator:</strong> You can access all functions, including purchasing new valet services, parking cars, and providing excellent customer service to grow your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > We are two friends developed this game hope you will like and enjoy! Your support means a lot! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like this game, don't forget to add the full version to your wishlist. Exciting advanced features and endless fun await you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be the Owner:</strong> Own and manage new valet businesses within a limited area, unlocking opportunities for growth and profit. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customer Feedback:</strong> Collect and act on customer feedback to enhance your services and boost customer satisfaction.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parking Expertise:</strong> Master the art of parking to maximize efficiency and provide a smooth experience, attracting more customers.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061070/extras/a081678dce3a0bf8b196ecd2e5811a42.avif?t=1739554538\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061070/extras/c0ff05a0d33a2ad96b6762e4650af90a.poster.avif?t=1739554538\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061070/extras/c0ff05a0d33a2ad96b6762e4650af90a.webm?t=1739554538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item